                                                                                                                                    },
                                                                                                                          "author":  "Selene",
                                                                                                                          "pages":  [
                                                                                                                                        "{\"text\":\"Always mark the red bottles. A draught of Healing can mend a cut, but it will not mend a burnt tongue.\"}",
                                                                                                                                        "{\"text\":\"Swiftness needs sugar. Water Breathing needs pufferfish. The mix curdles if heated too long. I tried it on a stray cat; it hissed and dove into the basin without fear.\"}"
